commit.message:
common.opt (flto-report): Do not mark as Optimization.

2012-05-04  Richard Guenther  <rguenther@suse.de>

	* common.opt (flto-report): Do not mark as Optimization.

	lto/
	* lang.opt (fwpa): Do not mark as Optimization.
	(fltrans): Likewise.

	* gcc.dg/lto/pr53214_0.c: New testcase.

From-SVN: r187151
